Cuno's appointment as chancellor is approved by all members of the coalition, due to his reputation of a technocrat.

- @ministries: First, we must select our ministries.

@marx_center_right_chancellor
title: Wilhelm Marx for Chancellor.
subtitle: Wilhelm Marx is a respected member of the <span style="color: #000000;">Center Party</span>.
