Marx's appointment as chancellor is approved by all members of the coalition, due to his reputation of a politician of compromise.

- @ministries: First, we must select our ministries.





  

@ministries

We can pick from any number of ministries. Controlling a ministry allows us to directly effect policy in that area.

- #mins_1922
- #drop_mins_1922

